# =============== Unity-specific generated files to IGNORE ===============
# These files are generated by Unity and should generally NOT be committed to Git.

# Library folder: Contains asset import metadata, cached files, and platform-specific data.
# This is usually the largest folder and should almost always be ignored.
# Unity 프로젝트를 열면 자동으로 다시 생성됩니다.
Library/

# Temp folder: Temporary files created by Unity during compilation and asset processing.
Temp/

# Obj folder: Intermediate object files generated during compilation (often by IDEs).
Obj/

# Builds folder: Compiled game builds for various platforms.
# 면접관이 바로 실행할 수 있도록 '빌드 결과물'은 포함하지 않습니다.
Builds/
*.apk
*.aab
*.xapk
*.ipa
*.exe
*.dmg
*.app
*.xcdetour
*.xctest
*.xcode
*.app.dSYM
*.pdb
*.psym
*.js
*.html
*.wasm

